events.name: 届かない荷物/炭鉱夫の誘引自動実行

parameters:
Coal Miner Zuro: Welcome to the office. Since the boss
collapsed, I've been using this place freely.

Coal Miner Zuro: I can mess around with the books as much as
I want! Hehehe, there aren't many people here who can do
calculations.
Thief Nora: Please...h-h-hand over the ore.
Coal Miner Zuro: You have a nice body.

Coal Miner Zuro: Hey, missy, you're not a virgin, huh? I can
tell, your scent reeks of a pervert.

Coal Miner Zuro: Ehehe, if you weren't interested, you
wouldn't have come this far with my invitation, right?

Coal Miner Zuro: The work here is very stressful, so just
lend me your body for a little while, that's all I need.
Thief Nora: Will you absolutely... keep your promise?

Coal Miner Zuro: Ehehe, of course! Leave everything to me,
young lady. You'll have a great time too.

Coal Miner Zuro: If you don't resist... does that mean
you're giving me your consent to proceed...?
Would you like to skip the adult scene?

Coal Miner Zuro: This was the place where I was going to be
exploited.
Thief Nora: P-Please... give me what you promised.

Coal Miner Zuro: Come back anytime, I'm always hungry for
women.
Do you want to skip the adult scene?
Miner Zuro: Hehe, I'm glad you came.

Miner Zuro: It's meaningless if I have the power to
manipulate the books but no use for it... So, come on, join
me.
